$interpreted: Toyokuni: Attention! They're incoming!
Toyokuni: Brace yourselves!!
Poisoned Beast Warrior: GRAAHH!!
Toyokuni: The Monster of Judgment's here! Use the Udumbara powder!
Yonghyeon: Ugh... mngh... Whatever's left of it.
Toyokuni: We'll hold the position here. You take care of the barrier stones.
Sione: ...I won't let you down!
Toyokuni: For the homeland!!
Frenzied Beast Warrior: For the homeland!!
Sione: Is that the barrier stone?
Tica: Guh... The Monster of Judgment's poison's wafting in...
Yonghyeon: Hurry it up, I don't know how much longer this Udumbara powder's gonna last.
Tica: Ooh, what's written here... Looks like a Rune, but not quite... Tica's on the case!
Tica: Going by that Qilin tome—and Tica's awesome intellect, too—it seems... you've got to... do something a little like... this?
Sione: It worked! Now the next one!
Sione: Waah...!
Yonghyeon: You okay?
Sione: I'm fine, but this poison gas is getting thicker by the minute...
Tica: Wah! That was close...
Yonghyeon: I see we couldn't get all the monsters out after all... I wonder how it looks from outside the city walls?
Sione: We'll just have to trust that they're okay. Don't get distracted now!
Tica: This stone's similar to the last one, but not quite...
Tica: Oohh~ I got it! With a jiggle here and a poke there, it should...
Tica: Success!
Sione: Let's get out of here!
Yonghyeon: ...Is anyone else feeling tired and heavy... or is it just me...
Sione: We're nearly there, just hold on...
Tica: Just a little further...
Tica: ...Last one. Watch me ace this!!
Tica: I... d-did... it...
Toyokuni: GRAAGH!!!
Toyokuni: It's... not... over...
Toyokuni: ...What the!?
Juan-Yun: (It's not possible... That's the Rune circle I devised myself...!)
Toyokuni: Ngh... guh!!! Hah!!!
Toyokuni: Almost... gah...
Toyokuni: Yonghyeon... You did it... We're...
Yonghyeon: Yes, we're gonna pull through... we're gonna...
Juan-Yun: (...What a headache. Did they copy my Rune? I didn't see that coming...)
Toyokuni: Look, Juan-Yun, the East is saved...
Juan-Yun: Yes, you're about to accomplish something the likes of which have never before been seen. And now I have no choice left.
Toyokuni: Huh?
Juan-Yun: I'll have to decide your fate myself.
